thread.title: Laura Patton

author: Laura Patton
title: Laura Patton
text: Munchery is a fabulous service for any busy family. You get healthy, daily, cooked meals delivered to your door step. Being a single mom of 2 boys, I want them to have healthy home cooked meals but I just don't have the time with working fulltime to do it all. We have Munchery delivered ~1x a week and all are happy as I can pick a different meal for every person.
